    public abstract class AsyncDatabaseConnector<T extends BusinessEntity>
extends android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.Void,java.lang.Void,java.lang.String>
implements DatabaseConnector
    Generic connector to a database. This class gives an interface to communicate with a database. It needs the URL of the server-side script that generates and handles the data.
